collapse.paragraphs:
 The addition and multiplication operations in $\mathbb{Q}(\alpha)$
are those associated with $\mathbb{R}$, in other words:
\begin{multline*}
(c_0 + c_1 \alpha + c_2 \alpha^2) + (b_0 + b_1 \alpha + b_2 \alpha^2)\\
= (c_0 + b_0) + (c_1 + b_1)\alpha + (c_2 + b_2)\alpha^2,
\end{multline*}
